{"about_the_game":"&quot;Saddle Up and Drive&quot; is a game set in the 1970s, where you play as the reckless nephew of an old car driver, now an alcoholic deeply in debt.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/extras/GIF_ING-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1733913334\" /><br><br>Find a way to earn your daily wage: smuggle (but don't get caught!), make good deals, or help the community.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/extras/Multimissione-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1733913334\" /><br><br>You can participate in various challenges, winning a lot of cash if you're capable.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/extras/gareggiamenti.gif?t=1733913334\" /><br><br>A multitude of different vehicles await you, each with its own peculiar characteristics. Choose the most suitable vehicle for the mission you intend to undertake!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/extras/Comparativo_1.gif?t=1733913334\" /><br><br>Explore a vast open world, consisting of 4 large maps of about 50 km\u00b2 each, plus a lot of extra levels!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/extras/MondoAperto.gif?t=1733913334\" /><br><br>And remember! This game is best played with a controller, but you can still use a mouse and keyboard.<br>Saddle Up and Drive is constantly being developed. Stay updated! Click 'Follow' on this page!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/extras/GiornoNotte_24.gif?t=1733913334\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733913334","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati